From d8a376b7b5f599472920620fc7b84bcda6c92aa8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Thadeu Lima de Souza Cascardo <cascardo@igalia.com>
Date: Thu, 7 Nov 2024 10:33:19 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 50/97] wifi: rtlwifi: rtl8192se: rise completion of firmware
