From f757327c4ce69f9d654aa43889c8c14035090d14 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Manivannan Sadhasivam <manivannan.sadhasivam@linaro.org>
Date: Thu, 5 Dec 2024 22:20:28 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 86/97] cpufreq: qcom: Fix qcom_cpufreq_hw_recalc_rate() to
